"use strict";(self.webpackChunkblog=self.webpackChunkblog||[]).push([[5672],{29913:(e,o,a)=>{a.r(o),a.d(o,{data:()=>c});const c={key:"v-4b649824",path:"/linux/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE.html",title:"Linux中配置环境变量",lang:"en-US",frontmatter:{date:"2021/12/20 16:20",title:"Linux中配置环境变量",tag:["linux","path","环境变量"],categories:["linux"]},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"环境变量",slug:"环境变量",children:[]}],git:{updatedTime:1654857597e3,contributors:[{name:"qsyyke",email:"2291308094@qq.com",commits:1}]}}},19517:(e,o,a)=>{a.r(o),a.d(o,{default:()=>s});const c=(0,a(66252).uE)('<p>在Linux中配置环境变量，这里以配置java环境变量为例</p><ol><li><p>下载jdk的<code>rpm</code>包或者是<code>.tar.gz</code></p></li><li><p>在<code>/opt</code>目录下，新建<code>jdk</code>，通常<code>/opt</code>目录存放的就是我们安装的程序</p></li><li><p>使用<code>ftp</code>工具将<code>.tar.gz</code>包上传到<code>/opt/ jdk</code>目录，并使用<code>tar -zxvf xxx</code>进行解压</p><blockquote><p>这里我在<code>xshell</code>中进行解压的时候报错，但是直接进入Linux桌面，运行<code>tar -zxvf xxx</code>并没有报错</p></blockquote></li><li><p>将解压后的文件移动到<code>/usr/local/jdk</code>里面</p><blockquote><p>通常<code>/usr/local/</code>目录就是存放我们的安装程序，和window上的<code>Program Files</code>文件夹一样</p></blockquote></li><li><p>进入<code>/etc/profile</code>编写环境变量</p></li><li><p>运行<code>source /etc/profile</code>，使环境变量生效</p></li></ol><h2 id="环境变量" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#环境变量" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 环境变量</h2><p>Linux中的环境变量在<code>/etc/profile</code>文件中进行编写</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token builtin class-name">export</span> <span class="token assign-left variable">JAVA_HOME</span><span class="token operator">=</span>/usr/local/jdk/jdk1.8\n<span class="token builtin class-name">export</span> <span class="token assign-left variable"><span class="token environment constant">PATH</span></span><span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token variable">$JAVA_HOME</span>/bin:<span class="token environment constant">$PATH</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><div class="custom-container warning"><p class="custom-container-title">WARNING</p><p>export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin<code>:$PATH</code>，当我们当初<code>PATH</code>的时候，一定要加上高亮部分，如果你像这样<code>export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin</code>，那么最终的环境变量里面就只有<code>/usr/local/jdk/jdk1.8/bin</code>，你可以将<code>:</code>想成是一个字符串相加</p></div>',6),n={},s=(0,a(83744).Z)(n,[["render",function(e,o){return c}]])}}]);